# Find the service which makes it possible to run specific tasks following
#	a regular schedule

cron / crontab

# Cron: The software utility cron is a time-based job scheduler.
#	Users that set up and maintain software environments use cron to schedule jobs 
#	(commands or shell scripts) to run periodically at fixed times, dates, or intervals
# https://www.ostechnix.com/a-beginners-guide-to-cron-jobs/